OL,3,CSystem-wide change needed to improve
OL,4,Cmaternity care in Northern Ireland `
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FHer report said that many women and
OL,8,Ftheir partners had described
OL,9,F"unacceptable experiences" which
OL,10,Fcontributed to "physical and emotional
OL,11,Fharm, sometimes causing long-lasting
OL,12,Fdistress".
OL,14,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt has
OL,15,Fresponded by announcing that a new
OL,16,Fmaternity and neonatal partnership
OL,17,Fwill be established to drive forward
OL,18,Fimprovements in care.
