OL,7,FThe report, Enabling Safe Quality
OL,8,FMidwifery Services and Care in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, was commissioned by
OL,10,Fthe Department of Health following a
OL,11,Fcoroner's court hearing into the death
OL,12,Fof a baby during birth in March 2017.
OL,14,FChristine McCleery's son Jaxon McVey
OL,15,Fwas born dead at the Royal Victoria
OL,16,FHospital after she was transferred
OL,17,Ffrom Lagan Valley Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
