OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FProf Renfrew said her review has found
OL,8,Fboth "serious weaknesses and real
OL,9,Fstrengths" in the current provision of
OL,10,Fmidwifery and wider maternity care for
OL,11,Fmothers and their babies.
OL,13,FShe said: "It proposes an ambitious
OL,14,Fevidence-based plan to transform
OL,15,Fmaternity services for all women,
OL,16,Fbabies and families and to improve
OL,17,Fsafety and quality and tackle
OL,18,Finequalities across Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@pD@FOUqD@JO]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
