OL,3,CSystem-wide change needed to improve
OL,4,Cmaternity care in Northern Ireland `
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"It includes requirements for the safe
OL,8,Fprovision of community midwifery units
OL,9,Fand home births, regional strategic
OL,10,Fdevelopments to support staff and
OL,11,Fensure safe, quality and equitable
OL,12,Fcare and services, improved data and
OL,13,Fmonitoring, and building for the
OL,14,Ffuture.
OL,16,F"Key requirements include acceptance
OL,17,Fby senior leaders that radical change
OL,18,Fis needed, together with investment
OL,19,Fthat reflects the level of need.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
