OL,7,F` A reconfigured relationship with
OL,8,Fwomen, families and communities,
OL,9,Fensuring respectful personalised care
OL,10,Ffor all and a genuine voice in shaping
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,F` A consistent, region-wide, evidence-
OL,14,Finformed approach to planning,
OL,15,Ffunding, standards, provision,
OL,16,Fmonitoring, and review of maternity
OL,17,Fand neonatal services.
