OL,7,F` Improving clinical, psychological,
OL,8,Fand cultural safety and equity for
OL,9,Fwomen, babies and families across the
OL,10,Fwhole continuum of care and in all
OL,11,Fsettings.
OL,13,F` Changing the prevailing work culture
OL,14,Fto implement an enabling environment
OL,15,Ffor all staff and managers, including
OL,16,Fensuring midwives are represented at
OL,17,Fsenior management levels, tackling
OL,18,Fsilo working, and developing an open
OL,19,Flearning culture at every level of the
OL,20,Fsystem.
