OL,7,FMr Nesbitt said: "My department is
OL,8,Fcommitted to continuing a major
OL,9,Fprogramme of work on improving
OL,10,Fmaternity and neonatal safety across
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland."
OL,13,FHe added: "The new maternity and
OL,14,Fneonatal partnership when established
OL,15,Fwill be tasked with implementing a
OL,16,Fconsolidated regional action plan
OL,17,Fincluding the overseeing of action on
OL,18,Frecommendations from Professor Renfrew.
