OL,3,CSystem-wide change needed to improve
OL,4,Cmaternity care in Northern Ireland `
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"This will only be properly effective
OL,8,Fthrough a multi-disciplinary approach
OL,9,Fthat keeps women and babies at the
OL,10,Fcentre of everything we do.
OL,12,F"Maternity services in Northern
OL,13,FIreland have undoubtedly been under
OL,14,Fintense pressure, not least in
OL,15,Frelation to staffing.
OL,17,F"The same, unfortunately, can be said
OL,18,Ffor services right across health and
OL,19,Fsocial care.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
