OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"I want to make very clear that
OL,8,Fimproving maternity and neonatal
OL,9,Fservices is an immediate area of focus
OL,10,Ffor my department and for me
OL,11,Fpersonally.
OL,13,F"Professor Renfrew has found both
OL,14,Fserious weaknesses and real strengths
OL,15,Fin the current provision of midwifery
OL,16,Fand wider maternity care for mothers
OL,17,Fand their babies.
OL,19,F"We need to both build on these
OL,20,Fstrengths and systematically address
OL,21,Fthe weaknesses.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
